        h4.subheader Step 3. Development
        p Using a front-end framework (
          a(href="http://foundation.zurb.com" title="zurb foundation 5 website") Zurb Foundation 5
          | ), I layed out Michael's website and set up a staging site for Michael's review and for user testing.

